            <p>本文用於記錄主流粵語聲母“n”和“l”對立時各所轄者，但不包括容易寫出漢字的，如「你」「能」等，此類字聲母大多可由普通話簡單推出。因此，本文主要關注一般不出現在書面語的詞彙。</p>
            <p>下表中，<b>記音</b>列可能有兩列，此時前一列是綜合音，可忽略；<br>
            有些詞可能二聲母皆可，本文不置可否。</p>
            <p><b>字頭</b>列高亮者<b>不</b>代表本字或正字，而只是基於音、義來選出的相對較爲合理的字；併隨後的小號漢字可分別理解爲「優先字形」及「候選字形」；<br>
            <i>斜體者</i>代表該詞可能不出現在廣州話中，本文保留作爲參考；<br>
                以「Ｘ」表記的字頭表示本文未對該詞指定優先字形。</p>


<table border="1">
<caption>聲母 “n” 與 “l” 轄字表</caption>
<tr><th style="width: 2.5em;">韻母</th>
    <th style="width: 2.5em;">聲調</th>
    <th style="width: 2.5em;">聲母</th>
    <th colspan="2">記音</th>
    <th style="width: 4em;">字頭</th>
    <th>釋義</th></tr>



    <tr><td rowspan="20">aa</td><td rowspan="4">1</td><td rowspan="3" class="A">n</td><td colspan='2'>naa1</td><td><span class='head'>拏</span><span class='sub'><small>𠸎</small></span></td><td class='mean'>①連詞，與：『我～渠食緊飯』；②替，幫：『我～你做』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>naa1</td><td><span class='head'>𪐀</span><span class='sub'><small>拏𠸎</small></span></td><td class='mean'>①粘貼：～墻紙；②相關連：～更｜～褦</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>naa1</td><td><span class='head'>𤸻</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①疤；②補丁</td></tr>
<tr><td class="B">l</td><td>laa1</td><td><b>laa1<br>la1</b></td><td><span class='head'>啦</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>語氣詞</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="6">2</td><td rowspan="2" class="A">n</td><td colspan='2'>naa2</td><td><span class='head'>俹</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>〔～簁〕作事苟且而不精細：你做事可唔可以唔好咁～</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>naa2</td><td><span class='head'>乸</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>雌性：雞～｜～型(娘娘腔)</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="7" class="B">l</td><td colspan='2'>laa2<br>laai2</td><td><span class='head'>揦</span><span class='sub'><small>瀬</small></span></td><td class='mean'>遭遇：～嘢(遇上麻煩)</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laa2</td><td><span class='head'>揦</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>抓、抓拿（一隻手拿握不能完全包住的物體）：『～隻蘿蔔』｜『～～埋一䊆』｜『一手～落去，至攞得幾粒花生』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laa2</td><td><span class='head'>揦</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①挽起，拉起：～衫袖；②攬，收回，使聚攏：～成一堆</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laa2</td><td><span class='head'>揦</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>皮膚、粘膜、傷口等受強烈刺激或侵蝕而感到疼痛或者體內的絞痛：『我心～住～住』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="3">3</td><td colspan='2'>laa3</td><td><i><span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>①〔～口〕喫到油炸辛辣食物喉嚨上火想嚥口水的感覺；②〔油～〕油渣；③變味</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laa3</td><td><span class='head'>喇</span><span class='sub'><small>嘑嚹</small></span></td><td class='mean'>句尾語氣詞</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laa3/le3</td><td><span class='head'>罅</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>縫隙，裂痕</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="6">4</td><td rowspan="3" class="A">n</td><td colspan='2'>naa4</td><td><i><span class='head'>那</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>地名用字，水田⟨壯語：naz⟩：～坡</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>naa4</td><td><span class='head'>嗱</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①豎中指時的附帶嘆詞，表達鄙視；②（對某人）豎中指：『～佢』；③表拒絕否定對方時的語氣詞</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>naa4</td><td><span class='head'>嗱</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>嘆詞，表指示，引起別人的注意：『～，幾多！』｜『～，睇了喂！』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="6" class="B">l</td><td colspan='2'>laa4</td><td><span class='head'></span><span class='sub'><small>𪢘喇</small></span></td><td class='mean'>表示詢問某種情況是否發生：『王伯䎺～？』｜『啲人走澌～？』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laa4</td><td><span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>〔大～～〕數額大：～幾千文</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laa4</td><td><span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>〔～～聲〕〔～～臨〕叫別人快點，麻利地：『～清数』</td></tr>
<tr><td>5</td><td colspan='2'>laa5</td><td><span class='head'>藞</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>〔～䕢〕髒亂</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="13">aai</td><td rowspan="2">1</td><td colspan='2'>laai1</td><td><span class='head'>拉</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>逮捕：〖～人兼封屋〗(逮捕人同時查封屋子)｜『～晒佢哋返差館』(把他們全都逮捕，並送到公安局)</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laai1</td><td><span class='head'>孻</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>最末：～尾｜～屘</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">2</td><td class="A">n</td><td colspan='2'>naai2</td><td><i><span class='head'>恁</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>遠指，那</td></tr>
<tr><td class="B">l</td><td colspan='2'>laai2</td><td><span class='head'>𦧺</span><span class='sub'><small>舐</small></span></td><td class='mean'>（用力）舔起，用舌頭掃</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="3">3</td><td class="A">n</td><td colspan='2'>naai3</td><td><span class='head'>艿</span><span class='sub'><small>𠮨褦𧜵</small></span></td><td class='mean'>①牽連，連帶：『佢講白話～到一啲北方口音』；②連帶刮擦：『佢坐單車陣時捱台細車～到，不過好彩冇受傷 』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="11" class="B">l</td><td colspan='2'>laai3?</td><td><i><span class='head'></span><span class='sub'><small>㓯</small></span></i></td><td class='mean'>解開：～開包装</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laai3</td><td><span class='head'>癩</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>麻風病，或癬疥等皮膚病：～渣</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">4</td><td colspan='2'>laai4</td><td><span class='head'>疧</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>形容（因病等）軟弱無力的樣子：軟～～｜腰骨～～</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laai4</td><td><span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>長貌：長～｜～～kaai4kaai4</td></tr>
<tr><td>5</td><td colspan='2'>laai5</td><td><i><span class='head'>酹</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>傾倒液體：『～啲油落鑊』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="3">6</td><td colspan='2'>laai6</td><td><span class='head'>攋</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>（因忘記而）遺落</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laai6</td><td><span class='head'>賴</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>怪罪：『～我囉？』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laai6</td><td><span class='head'>瀨</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>失禁：～屎</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="3">aak</td><td>1</td><td colspan='2'>laak1</td><td><i><span class='head'>Ｘ</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>擬聲詞：『柴燒到～～聲』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">3</td><td colspan='2'>laak3</td><td><i><span class='head'></span><span class='sub'><small>㔏</small></span></i></td><td class='mean'>裂開</td></tr>
<tr><td>laak3</td><td><b>laak3<br>lak3<br>la3</b></td><td><span class='head'>嘞</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>句尾語氣詞，大體同「喇」，口氣略輕的完成體助詞：『大家都嚟齊～』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="7">aam</td><td rowspan="2">1</td><td class="A">n</td><td colspan='2'>naam1</td><td><i><span class='head'>喃</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>①喃喃自語；②誦讀：～齋｜～經</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2" class="B">l</td><td colspan='2'>laam1<br>lem1</td><td><i><span class='head'>爁</span><span class='sub'><small>燫</small></span></i></td><td class='mean'>①火焰燎著：『捱火尾～到』｜～黑；②用火燒去動物的毛：～豬毛</td></tr>
<tr><td>2</td><td colspan='2'>laam2</td><td><span class='head'>攬</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>摟抱：～抱</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">3</td><td>n/l</td><td>naam3<br>laam3</td><td><b>naam3</b></td><td><span class='head'>𨂾</span><span class='sub'><small>𨈇檻</small></span></td><td class='mean'>①跨：～步；②量詞，一步的距離：幾～腳遠</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="3" class="A">n</td><td colspan='2'>naam3</td><td><span class='head'>揇</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>量詞，手掌張開後大拇指尖和中指間的距離：一～</td></tr>
<tr><td>4</td><td colspan='2'>naam4</td><td><span class='head'>蚺</span><span class='sub'><small>蝻蚦</small></span></td><td class='mean'>一類體型巨大的蛇，大蟒蛇：～蛇</td></tr>
<tr><td>5</td><td colspan='2'>naam5</td><td><span class='head'>腩</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>肚子上和近肋處的鬆軟肌肉，亦指用此種肉做成的菜餚</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="8">aan</td><td rowspan="3">1</td><td rowspan="3" class="B">l</td><td colspan='2'>laan1</td><td><span class='head'>蘭</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>譯音字：荷～｜～豆(荷蘭豆)</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laan1</td><td><span class='head'>欄</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>（飼養禽畜的）圍欄</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laan1</td><td><span class='head'>躝</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>叫人滾蛋</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">2</td><td class="A">n</td><td colspan='2'>naan3</td><td><span class='head'></span><span class='sub'><small>㫱赧𧕴</small></span></td><td class='mean'>皮膚因被蚊蟲叮咬或過敏所起的疙瘩：蚊～</td></tr>
<tr><td class="B">l</td><td colspan='2'>laan2</td><td><span class='head'></span><span class='sub'><small>爛</small></span></td><td class='mean'>自認十分如何如何而令人厭惡：～叻｜『你就～大方，係我出錢㗎！』｜『佢～熱情噉，我先唔睬佢』｜『使乜～正經啊！』</td></tr>
<tr><td>4</td><td class="A">n</td><td colspan='2'>naan4</td><td><i><span class='head'>難</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>境況不佳：『近排真係～噢』｜～頂｜～抵</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">6</td><td rowspan="4" class="B">l</td><td colspan='2'>laan6</td><td><span class='head'>糷</span><span class='sub'><small>爛</small></span></td><td class='mean'>飯爛相粘著，一般寫爛</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laan6</td><td><span class='head'>爛</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①破舊，雜亂：～嘢；②慣常、沉迷做某事（多貶義）：～耍</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">aang</td><td>1</td><td colspan='2'>laang1</td><td><span class='head'>唥</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>羊毛，毛織品⟨葡語：lã，法語：laine⟩：～線｜～衫</td></tr>
<tr><td>6</td><td colspan='2'>laang6</td><td><span class='head'>唥</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>〔冚唪～〕全部</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="7">aap</td><td rowspan="5">3</td><td class="A">n</td><td colspan='2'>naap3</td><td><i><span class='head'>衲</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>泛指連綴：𪐀～(關連)｜～釦(魔術貼、子母貼)</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="4" class="B">l</td><td colspan='2'>laap3</td><td><span class='head'>蠟</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>油光發亮：～靚</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laap3</td><td><span class='head'>䁽</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>快速地看，粗略地看：～一眼</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laap3</td><td><span class='head'>擸</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>收拾使之合一，使合攏，包攬：『佢一隻人～齊所有訂單』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laap3</td><td><span class='head'>擸</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①攬抱：『～住堆衫褲』；②擄掠：『～嘢返屋』｜『打工～夠十萬至返屋』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">6</td><td class="A">n</td><td colspan='2'>naap6</td><td><i><span class='head'>納</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>〔～袋〕衣服的口袋</td></tr>
<tr><td class="B">l</td><td colspan='2'>laap6</td><td><span class='head'>垃</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>〔～雜〕雜亂：『冇食咁多～嘢』</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="7">aat</td><td rowspan="3">3</td><td rowspan="2" class="A">n</td><td colspan='2'>naat3</td><td><i><span class='head'>捺</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>用手按、蹭：～手印｜『佢將鼻屎～在我身上』｜『～死隻蟻子』</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>naat3</td><td><span class='head'>焫</span><span class='sub'><small>爇</small></span></td><td class='mean'>①泛指用器物燙，烙：～着(點燃)；②（器物等）炙熱</td></tr>
<tr><td class="B">l</td><td colspan='2'>laat3</td><td><span class='head'>瘌</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>①指破皮，被勒或者曬到皮膚焦，皮膚會又辣又痛：『曬久皮膚會～痛』；②擦破（皮膚）：～皮</td></tr>
<tr><td>4</td><td class="A">n</td><td colspan='2'>naat4</td><td><i><span class='head'>𪞗</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>形容黏或混濁：𪐌～～｜粈～～｜nam1～～</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="3">6</td><td rowspan="6" class="B">l</td><td colspan='2'>laat6</td><td><span class='head'>邋</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>〔～遢〕不淨，髒</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laat6</td><td><span class='head'>辣</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>一種刺激性味道：～薑</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan='2'>laat6</td><td><span class='head'>迾</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>量詞，列⟨壯語：lad⟩</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="6">aau</td><td>1</td><td colspan='2'>laau1</td><td><span class='head'>僗</span><span class='sub'><small>撈</small></span></td><td class='mean'>指北方的：講～｜～佬</td></tr>
<tr><td>2</td><td colspan='2'>laau2</td><td><span class='head'>摎</span><span class='sub'></span></td><td class='mean'>〔～攪〕做事不認真</td></tr>
<tr><td>3</td><td colspan='2'>laau3</td><td><i><span class='head'>𱃭</span><span class='sub'></span></i></td><td class='mean'>遺漏：睇～眼｜～過(未注意而跳過)</td></tr>
<tr><td rowspan="2">4</td><td class="A">n</td><td colspan='2'>naau4</td><td><span class='head'>橈</span><span class='sub'><small>褭</small></span></td><td class='mean'>形容柔，亦見“褭”：～～</td></tr>
